title: Ep. 301 "Pre Cum Babies United" ft. Mandii B & Bridget Kelly of See The Thing Is Podcast
description:
This week we're joined by the hosts of See The Thing Is Podcast, Mandii B & Bridget Kelly. We debate on what happens when you actually get pregnant by precum, ruining relationships before they begin, and men listening to our shows even when we tell them not to.
